2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆開個機箱逐樣check<br />\n先拆顯示卡用內顯<br />\n重插過Ram(亦試過用一條ram)<br />\n重插過CPU同散熱風扇<br />\n換埋另一隻火牛試<br />\n反覆試 10次都有2-3次boot到部機<br />\n好撚奇怪<br />\n我估應該係底板壞左<br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該關天氣突然變凍的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：<span style=\"color: red;\">砌</span>過部新<span style=\"color: red;\">機</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>又唔洗砌過部掛 轉第2塊老母版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />highlight錯左喇"},{"pid":"719c600375b9c1998746fd1948126792c7a10aa2","tid":1768043,"uid":111278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b067b823e6b3c14f7fef6795dae94610e3b1792b","tid":1768043,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"拎擦膠擦下條ram"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"試左鳥，有保養去左擺底條女 話等通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}